However, keep in mind that the drawing system of Swing/AWT will decide really quick that is must redraw everything. GUI actions like focus switch or resize can result in the Swing/AWT system thinking &quot;Well, what I am currently showing is not current anymore, I have to redraw everything&quot; and calls `repaint()` without any limits.

